{
  "title": "ISic000194. Funerary inscription for Marcia, wife of Lucius Mammius",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa, Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prag 2023-07-05, in the depositi of the Museo Civico, room 1, rack 8, shelf 1.</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"dis\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"\">dis</span>  <span data-text=\"manibus\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"\">ṃ[anibus]</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"Marciae\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">Marciae</span> · <span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">..</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"piae\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"\">piae</span> ❦ <span data-text=\"vixit\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"\">v(ixit)</span> ❦ <span data-text=\"annis\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"\">a(nnis)</span> ❦ XX [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"Lucius\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"\">L(ucius)</span> ❦ <span data-text=\"Mammius\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"\">Mammius</span> ❦ <span data-text=\"V\" data-n=\"90\" data-lemma=\"\">V</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"uxori\" data-n=\"100\" data-lemma=\"\">uxor<span class=\"tall\" title=\"tall character: i\">i</span></span> ❦ <span data-text=\"castissimae\" data-n=\"110\" data-lemma=\"\">casṭ[issimae]</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa, Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prag 2023-07-05, in the depositi of the Museo Civico, room 1, rack 8, shelf 1.</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"dis\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"\">DIS</span><span data-text=\"manibus\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"\">.[......]</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"Marciae\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">MARCIAE</span>·<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">··</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"piae\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"\">PIAE</span>❦<span data-text=\"vixit\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"\">V</span>❦<span data-text=\"annis\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"\">A</span>❦XX[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"Lucius\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"\">L</span>❦<span data-text=\"Mammius\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"\">MAMMIUS</span>❦<span data-text=\"V\" data-n=\"90\" data-lemma=\"\">V</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"uxori\" data-n=\"100\" data-lemma=\"\">UXOR<span class=\"tall\" title=\"tall character: i\">I</span></span>❦<span data-text=\"castissimae\" data-n=\"110\" data-lemma=\"\">CAS.[.......]</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic000194_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-05\" src=\"ISic000194_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic000194.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-05\" src=\"ISic000194-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic000194_rear_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-05\" src=\"ISic000194_rear_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic000194_rear.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-05\" src=\"ISic000194_rear-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text from autopsy</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"1\">1: <span>Bivona: M[an(ibus)]; it is speculation as to whether \"Manibus\" was abbreviated or not, although the size of the letters makes it very likely</span>  </span><br></li><li><span class=\"2\">2: <span>The lower part of two vertical strokes are visible before the break.</span>  </span><br></li><li><span class=\"5\">5: <span>Little more than an initial serif is visible at the break</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>It is likely that the cognomen of the deceased is missing in line 2. In line 3 the absence of a mark of interpunctation after the final X suggests that there is nothing more missing on this line (which also speaks against a strictly centred and symmetrical text). The restoration of 'cast[issimae]' as already proposed by Mommsen in the final line seems very plausible and there are no realistic alternatives.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li></li><li> Mommsen 1883 <a href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/books/CILv10pII1883\" target=\"_blank\">7419</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589</a>  </li><li> Bivona 1994 117 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Deep regular v-cut letters in a fairly broad module, with simple serifs. Use of I longa, and most interpuncts are hederae (that in line 2 is a triangle).</p> Line 1  53  Line 2  37-40  Line 3  30-31  Line 4  26-28  Line 5  30-33 (I = 38)  Interlineation line 1 to 2  3  Interlineation line 2 to 3  5-6  Interlineation line 3 to 4  6-8  Interlineation line 4 to 5  6-10  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
